{"tid":195615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一度陷破產邊緣的樂視 臨時取消下周發佈會","createTime":"2017-04-10T17:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T01:14:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8f90a94be599e2547bc49a5b8d63e3f651f6de","tid":195615,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170407/56534517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170407%2F56534517&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Brr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=32f30bee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170407%2F56534517&h=e825d70e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170407/56534517</a><br />\n<br />\n樂視又出事！？雖然已獲融創﹙1918﹚注資168億元人民幣救亡，但樂視仍不時傳出財政問題。樂視香港周一發邀請指，將於下周二舉行國際級賽事發布會，但3日後，樂視突然通知取消下周的發佈，指「現階段部分新業務細節仍有待確定，原定於2017年4月11日舉行的發布會將會延後舉行。」發言人回應指，與財政問題無關。<br />\n<br />\n樂視原定下周二於荃灣嘉達環球中心的辦公室舉行發佈會，「LeSports HK首席執行官賴汝正將會向傳媒朋友宣布一項重要版權賽事之各項詳情，包括優惠收費組合及超強評述主持陣容」。樂視更指活動後可與嘉賓進行訪問，但今日下午就收到通知，指由於部分新業務細節仍有待確定。事件不禁令人聯想會否再出現財政問題，發言人回覆本報時就強調與財政問題無關。"},{"pid":"594a8c00d87125225b538819753fa5ee97da5310","tid":195615,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f097a983e68400d442acb86928d5a96efdfbf4","tid":195615,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:44:14.000Z","msg":"唔好執啊"},{"pid":"407fc914bc8643be0ee2ceed18145b2c3d12be1f","tid":195615,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T20:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好執啊</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n點解？"},{"pid":"74dc8b342e9c4df6a08cac6a05db21ac8fc2b57c","ti